<p>High quality paper selection criteria and a prompt review process will be ensured. The review will follow the standard Sadhana review process with all rules applied. The guest editors will be responsible for getting the reviews, and submitting their recommendations along with the reviews to the handling Associate Editor of sadhana, and the handling Associte Editor will then make final acceptance or rejection decisions and communicate with authors. To avoid conflicts of interest, the following rules will be emphasized:</p>
<ul>
	<li>A guest editor should not appear as author/co-author for more than two submissions to the Special Issue.</li>
	<li>The Associate editor appointed by the editorial board will assign reviewers to handle papers submitted by the guest editors.</li>
</ul>
